  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "CS1",
      "text": [
        "The sea is ink. The ship is a whisper. Above you, a crimson seagull circles like an omen.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "Placeholder Demo: This file exists so the story loads from the library. Full Crimson Seagull comes next." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "CS1A", "text": "Check the Lantern and descend below deck.", "to": "CS2" },
        { "id": "CS1B", "text": "Stand watch. Trust your instincts.", "to": "CS3" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CS2",
      "text": [
        "Below deck, you find a velvet-wrapped shape pulsing with heat: the Ember Crown.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "You gain: Ember Crown (Artifact)." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "CS2A", "text": "Take it. Accept whatever follows.", "to": "CS4" },
        { "id": "CS2B", "text": "Leave it and return above.", "to": "CS3" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CS3",
      "text": [
        "Wind snaps the sails. Somewhere in the dark, something answers the ship’s creak."
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "CS3A", "text": "Return to Main Menu.", "to": "MENU" },
        { "id": "CS3B", "text": "Restart Crimson Seagull.", "to": "CS1" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CS4",
      "text": [
        "The Ember Crown warms your palms. The crimson seagull screams once, like approval.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "whisper", "text": "A world notices when you wear its fire." }
      ],
      "choices": [
